    Associations
    The Associations interface provides methods to manage associations of a single consumption-domain zone to multiple vSphere clusters.

    The Associations interface provides methods to manage associations of a single consumption-domain zone to multiple vSphere clusters.

    The Status class contains information about the outcome of the method to add a set of vSphere clusters to a zone or the method to remove a set of vSphere clusters from a zone.
